Project Title: Responsive Portfolio Website

Description:
Create an engaging and responsive portfolio website with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Showcase your skills, projects, and personal information in a visually appealing and user-friendly manner. The website features a modern design, smooth scrolling navigation, toggle menu functionality, and a mobile-friendly layout. It incorporates Boxicons for icons and utilizes media queries to ensure optimal display on various screen sizes. Use this project to showcase your coding abilities and present your work to potential employers or clients.

Key Features:
- Responsive design that adapts to different screen sizes and devices.
- Smooth scrolling navigation for a seamless user experience.
- Toggle menu icon for improved mobile navigation.
- Boxicons integration for high-quality icons.
- Sections for introducing yourself, showcasing your projects, and detailing your skills.
- Customizable color scheme and typography to match your personal branding.
- Demonstrates HTML, CSS, and JavaScript skills.
- Ideal for aspiring developers looking to build a professional online presence.

Use this portfolio website project as a powerful tool to highlight your achievements and capabilities,
making a lasting impression on visitors. Whether you're a student, freelancer, or job seeker, 
this project provides a solid foundation for creating an effective online portfolio.
